                                        "},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"From 0 to 4 the values of the expression are 6, 3, 2 and 2; from that point the values are always 1, so we can do (2016-4+1)+6+3+2+2=2026"}]},{"type":"text","text":"



